k><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京在周五发表的采访中谈到了乌克兰的战争与和平、遗传学和人工智能进步的风险以及对世界大战的担忧。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:04:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/what-did-putin-say-war-peace-ww3-ai-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国经济困境加剧，投资银行准备迎接更多亚洲裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-woes-mount-investment-banks-brace-more-asia-job-cuts-2024-02-09/</link><description>猎头公司和银行家表示，今年西方投资银行在亚洲的裁员预计将增加。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 07:01:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-woes-mount-investment-banks-brace-more-asia-job-cuts-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>百度与联想达成第三笔中国人工智能智能手机交易</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</link><description>中国的百度与联想合作，将其生成式人工智能（AI）技术应用到联想的智能手机上，这是与手机制造商的最新合作，旨在为其人工智能模型寻求实际应用。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:48:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/baidu-partners-with-lenovo-third-china-ai-smartphone-deal-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：杜克能源将把中国电池巨头宁德时代从海军陆战队基地撤出</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</link><description>在国会的压力下，美国公用事业公司杜克能源公司计划退役中国电池制造商宁德时代在美国最大的海军陆战队基地之一生产的储能电池。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 05:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/duke-energy-remove-chinese-battery-giant-catl-marine-corps-base-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>美元走强抑制避险需求，金价持平</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五金价持平，中国市场因农历新年假期休市，而美元走强抵消了中东紧张局势引发的避险需求。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:49:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/gold-flat-safe-haven-demand-offsets-us-dollar-strength-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国新年旅游高峰进入高潮，中国增加了创纪录的火车数量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-year-travel-rush-kicks-into-high-gear-country-adds-record-number-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五，中国在一年一度的农历新年假期前夕进入了高潮，旅客们挤上火车和飞机返回家乡，与家人一起准备传统的团圆饭聚会。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 04:23:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-new-year-travel-rush-kicks-into-high-gear-country-adds-record-number-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>第三季度财报突显中国担忧，日产股价暴跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-q3-results-highlight-china-worries-competition-2024-02-09/</link><description>日产汽车 (Nissan Motor) 下调了本财年的销量预期，且对其中国业务感到担忧，周五该公司股价暴跌 11.7%，这可能是自 2001 年以来的最大跌幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 02:17:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nissan-shares-slump-q3-results-highlight-china-worries-competition-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>日经指数创新高，中国新年假期紧张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-09/</link><description>日本股市周五触及 34 年来的新高，世界股市有望连续第三周上涨，而利率预期的调整则导致日元跌至两个月低点，澳元和新西兰元则走势相反。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 02:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国考虑采取限制措施将中国“智能汽车”拒之门外 - 彭博社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-considering-curbs-keep-chinese-smart-cars-out-country-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</link><description>彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道称，由于美国对数据安全的担忧日益加剧，拜登政府正在考虑限制进口中国“智能汽车”及相关零部件。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:58:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/us-considering-curbs-keep-chinese-smart-cars-out-country-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>交易员调整利率押注，美元与日元展开较量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-near-10-week-low-dollar-buoyant-traders-adjust-rate-bets-2024-02-09/</link><description>周五美元连续第四周上涨，推动日元跌至 10 个月低点，交易员取消了对日本央行可能加息速度以及美联储降息速度的押注。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-near-10-week-low-dollar-buoyant-traders-adjust-rate-bets-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>泰国、马来西亚、新加坡希望通过免签旅游吸引中国人</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-malaysia-singapore-hope-lure-chinese-with-visa-free-travel-2024-02-09/</link><description>中国工程师兼航空爱好者魏猛正是新加坡、马来西亚和泰国旅游部门正在寻找的游客。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:10:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/thailand-malaysia-singapore-hope-lure-chinese-with-visa-free-travel-2024-02-09/</guid></item><item><title>英国基金经理阿什莫尔退出对中国恒大的押注 - 彭博新闻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-fund-manager-ashmore-exited-bet-china-evergrande-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</link><description>据彭博社周四援引知情人士的话报道，英国安石集团（Ashmore Group）曾是中国恒大集团海外债务的主要持有者，去年年底完全退出了对这家中国房地产开发商的投资。</description><pubDate>Fri, 09 Feb 2024 01:09:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/uk-fund-manager-ashmore-exited-bet-china-evergrande-bloomberg-news-2024-02-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>